{
  "stem": "19923.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- when I first saw him do that, or when I first recollected him doing that, even at my younger age, I thought it was a little imprudent, perhaps.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I knew that I have never done that in my life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But whether or not this was part of his upbringing or whether or not that this was the convention of the time, these are things that I do recollect of my father at an early life.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My mother I have also fond memories, but not-- my memories of my mother are of a woman that was under a lot of pressure and she had at times fainting spells.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And whether or not they were epileptic seizures or not, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I've asked members of my family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I've asked my uncle, my mother's younger brother, Herman Gottesdiener, now Charles Gordon, who passed away last year, whether or not she did have epileptic fits.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he said no, he thought it was mostly nervousness.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So my mother was, perhaps because the pressures of the time, having five children, living in a small-- small apartment, not having any amenities, and perhaps being responsible for the upbringing of five children, was a nervous woman and at times had nervous spells.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I know that she was a warm, affectionate woman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I know that she was a caring woman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I know that she loved all of us dearly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In terms of her background, she also was not a very educated woman.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And whatever knowledge I've acquired, if I have-- whatever I have acquired in my life has not been from anything that I can attribute to my mother or father in terms of exposure to culture, art, in terms of music.",
      "word_count": 40
    }
  ],
